These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
Transport: taxi, bus, tram
1. Transport:bus is on the right of Transport:tram##1
2. Transport:taxi is on the far right##1
3. Transport:taxi is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Transport   | tram | bus | taxi |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
City: nizza, hannover, marseilles
1. City:hannover is in an odd position##4
2. City:nizza is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| City   | nizza | marseilles | hannover |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: disaster, scientific, zombie
1. Movie-Genre:scientific is in an even position##4
2. Movie-Genre:scientific is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:zombie##3
3. Movie-Genre:zombie is on the right of Movie-Genre:scientific##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | scientific | zombie |

 #################################
 
